@startuml Sequence_Additional_Features

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Feature API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

== Wishlist ==
User -> Client: View product
User -> Client: Click add to wishlist
Client -> API: POST /api/wishlist
API -> DB: Add to wishlist
DB --> API: Item added
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show added message

User -> Client: View wishlist
Client -> API: GET /api/wishlist
API -> DB: Get wishlist items
DB --> API: Wishlist data
API --> Client: Return wishlist
Client --> User: Display wishlist

== Report Content ==
User -> Client: Click report
Client -> Client: Fill report form
Client -> API: POST /api/reports
API -> DB: Save report
DB --> API: Report saved
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Show confirmation

== View About/Community/Contact ==
User -> Client: Navigate to page
Client -> API: GET /api/pages/:pageType
API -> DB: Get page content
DB --> API: Page data
API --> Client: Return content
Client --> User: Display page

@enduml

